headline: Tractor Supply (TSCO) Valuation Check As Truist Downgrade Highlights Concerns On Sales And Growth
summary: Tractor Supply (TSCO) is back in focus after Truist Securities downgraded the stock, pointing to proprietary card data that suggests broad sales softness and persistent pressure on same store growth. See our latest analysis for Tractor Supply. Recent trading reflects that tension.
